These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Transport   | scooter | skateboard | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, magic-tricks, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Hobby   | sudoku | puzzles | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
City: edinburgh, nizza, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| City   | nizza | edinburgh | paris |

